# shelfd build context ignore list — SHELF-09.
#
# Build context is the repo root (see shelfd/Dockerfile). Anything
# listed here never crosses the docker daemon boundary, which keeps
# `docker build` from uploading multi-GB `target/` trees and speeds
# every iteration.

# --- Rust build artefacts (biggest win — hundreds of MB) -----------
target/
**/target/

# --- VCS / CI / tooling --------------------------------------------
.git/
.gitignore
.github/
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Non-build corners of the monorepo -----------------------------
benchmarks/
charts/
clients/
observability/
agents/
chaos/
runbooks/
infra/
tools/
docs/
SECURITY/

# --- Markdown + standalone docs — LICENSE/NOTICE kept by exclusion -
*.md
!LICENSE
!NOTICE

# --- OS / editor cruft ---------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# --- Secrets / local-only ------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Test fixtures & caches ----------------------------------------
/tmp-data
/.testdata
**/criterion/
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
node_modules/
